query:
SELECT a.id, a.title, a.trackCount, a.userId, a.createdAt,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tracks t WHERE t.albumId = a.id) as actual_track_count
FROM albums a
WHERE a.title LIKE '%Still Out Tonight%'
LIMIT 5;
